r `FPQ16ExpClampArrayToInputDomainChecked` in `src/math/intexp.HC` to apply checked per-lane domain clamping over Q16 vectors (`in[i] -> out[i]`) with shared scalar clamp semantics for upcoming WS1 vectorized exp kernels (WS1-02)\n- [x] IQ-164 Implement HolyC helper `FPQ16ExpFromClampedInputChecked` in `src/math/intexp.HC` to evaluate Q16 exp only for pre-clamped inputs (`EXP_Q16_MIN_INPUT <= x <= EXP_Q16_MAX_INPUT`) and expose checked BAD_PARAM contracts for vector callers that separate clamp and eval phases (WS1-02)\n- [x] IQ-165 Implement HolyC helper `FPQ16ExpArrayChecked` in `src/math/intexp.HC` to compute elementwise Q16 exp over arrays with checked pointer/count contracts and per-lane clamp+eval composition for softmax precompute paths (WS1-02)\n- [x] IQ-166 Add host-side parity harness `tests/test_intexp_exp_array_checked.py` validating clamp+eval array semantics, saturation edges, and BAD_PARAM/NULL_PTR surfaces against scalar reference composition (WS1-05)\n- [x] IQ-167 Implement HolyC helper `FPQ16ExpArrayFromClampedInputChecked` in `src/math/intexp.HC` to evaluate elementwise Q16 exp for pre-clamped vectors and fail fast on first out-of-domain lane without partial writes for split-phase softmax kernels (WS1-02)\n- [x] IQ-168 Implement HolyC helper `FPQ16ExpArrayCheckedNoAliasChecked` in `src/math/intexp.HC` to enforce non-aliasing (`input_q16 != output_q16`) with shared checked span math for callers that require strict source immutability during softmax staging (WS1-02)\n- [x] IQ-169 Implement HolyC helper `FPQ16SoftmaxExpPhaseFromPreclampedChecked` in `src/math/softmax.HC` to compute exp-lanes from pre-clamped logits by composing `FPQ16ExpArrayFromClampedInputChecked` and checked sum accumulation for split-phase softmax pipelines (WS1-03)\n- [x] IQ-170 Implement HolyC helper `FPQ16SoftmaxExpPhaseFromPreclampedNoAliasChecked` in `src/math/softmax.HC` to require disjoint input/output buffers while reusing shared checked span+sum logic for immutable-logit 